  <body>
    <p>The <uicontrol>Statistics</uicontrol> page is where you can see the number of page views and
      comments added for a site configuration. Users with a role of <i>Owner</i>, <i>Admin</i>, or
        <i>Moderator</i> can see the statistics for the site configuration. To reach this page,
      click the <uicontrol><image href="../img/ofb-StatisticsPage16.png" id="image_txz_51g_gjb"
        />Statistics</uicontrol> link in the left menu bar in the interface for the site
      configuration.</p>
